antic schemas for all MVP backend models. Do not touch landing page or GFF AI tools. Include create, update, list/read response schemas where useful for User, ClientAccount, Project, AgentOperation, DocumentItem, Invoice, SupportTicket, GovernanceItem. Include Auth schemas: LoginRequest, TokenResponse, CurrentUserResponse. Keep schemas simple. Use from_attributes or ORM mode depending on Pydantic version. Ensure schemas do not expose hashed_password. Keep response fields aligned with the Phase 4 frontend data needs. Run backend import check.\"\n865 |   },","success":true}],"durationMs":3}}
